OL,7,FA driver has been sentenced for
OL,8,Fcausing a road traffic collision which
OL,9,Fleft four people seriously injured.
OL,11,FNorman Chai, 66, from Woking in
OL,12,FSurrey, appeared at Exeter Crown Court
OL,13,Ffor sentence on Wednesday 3 July.
OL,15,FHe had pleaded guilty to four causing
OL,16,Fserious injury by dangerous driving
OL,17,Fcharges.
