OL,7,FHe was sentenced to two years in
OL,8,Fcustody suspended for two years,
OL,9,Ftagged for three months and ordered to
OL,10,Fpay a #2,000 fine by Recorder James
OL,11,FBromige.
OL,13,FChai was also banned from driving for
OL,14,Fthree years and ordered to take an
OL,15,Fextended test.
OL,17,FDuring the sentencing hearing, the
OL,18,Fcourt heard how on 26 November 2022 a
OL,19,Fthree vehicle collision occurred on
OL,20,Fthe A30 near Rawridge, Devon.
