OL,7,FThe driver of one of the vehicles
OL,8,Finvolved, Chai, was travelling to
OL,9,FCornwall for a holiday accompanied by
OL,10,Fhis wife and mother-in-law.
OL,12,FDespite wet driving conditions, Chai
OL,13,Fwent to overtake a HGV, so moving into
OL,14,Fa dedicated turning lane for opposing
OL,15,Ftraffic.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
