OL,7,FChai then violently pulled his vehicle
OL,8,Fback into his own lane before a
OL,9,Fcentral island, but in doing so lost
OL,10,Fcontrol of his vehicle and
OL,11,F'fishtailed' across into the path of
OL,12,Foncoming traffic before striking the
OL,13,Ffront of an oncoming Mitsubishi.
OL,15,FThe collision caused Chai's Vauxhall
OL,16,Fto rotate 180 degrees clockwise back
OL,17,Finto the westbound carriageway before
OL,18,Fcoming to rest.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
