OL,7,FThe Mitsubishi, unable to avoid Chai's
OL,8,Fvehicle, also rotated and came to
OL,9,Frest. A Kia Rio following the
OL,10,FMitsubishi was unable to avoid
OL,11,Fcolliding with its driver's side.
OL,13,FAs a result of the collision Chai, his
OL,14,Fwife and mother-in-law all suffered
OL,15,Fmultiple lacerations and fractures.
OL,17,FThe driver of the Mitsubishi also
OL,18,Fsustained fractures, as did the
OL,19,Fpassenger of the Kia Rio following the
OL,20,FMitsubishi.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
