OL,7,FIn interview Chai said that he
OL,8,Fbelieved he waited until there was
OL,9,Fenough room and time for him to
OL,10,Fovertake the HGV, but ended up losing
OL,11,Fcontrol.
OL,13,FHe added that with hindsight, he
OL,14,Fshouldn't have carried out the
OL,15,Fmanoeuvre.
OL,17,FSergeant Troy Bennett of the Serious
OL,18,FCollision Investigations Team said:
OL,19,F"Norman Chai's actions on the 26
OL,20,FNovember 2022 had catastrophic
OL,21,Fconsequences.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
