OL,7,F"His illegal overtake contravened
OL,8,Fdouble solid white lines, he travelled
OL,9,Fthrough the filter lane for oncoming
OL,10,Ftraffic and almost collided into a
OL,11,Fcentral traffic island before he lost
OL,12,Fcontrol.
OL,14,F"This was done during heavy rain with
OL,15,Fwet roads and was a highly dangerous
OL,16,Fand egregious manoeuvre resulting in
OL,17,Fserious injuries to five people,
OL,18,Fincluding Chai himself, occupants of
OL,19,Fhis own car, and those in the oncoming
OL,20,Fvehicles he struck.
