OL,7,F"The dashcam footage of the collision
OL,8,Freleased by us today demonstrates how
OL,9,Fquickly things can go devastatingly
OL,10,Fwrong when you drive dangerously.
OL,12,F"Devon and Cornwall Police are
OL,13,Fcommitted to reducing fatal and
OL,14,Fserious injury collisions on our roads
OL,15,Fand all drivers have a responsibility
OL,16,Fto drive carefully and appropriately."
